    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Idna Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Idna</application> module provides support
        for the Internationalized Domain Names in Applications (IDNA) protocol
        as specified in RFC 5891.
      </para>

      &lfs121_checked;

